{"title":"2.3构造函数和析构函数","uid":"348dd3874381c90e4fb4910c5c92f074","slug":"cpp2.3","date":"2022-01-17T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-21T05:14:58.843Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/cpp2.3.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/cpp/cover1.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"引言\"><a href=\"#引言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"引言\"></a>引言</h1><p>上一节中我们举了这样一个例子：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-C++\" data-language=\"C++\"><code class=\"language-C++\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\nclass MyClass&#123;\npublic:\n    int _a;\n    char _b;\n    int add()&#123;\n        return (_a+_b);\n    &#125;\n&#125;;\nint main()&#123;\n    MyClass m,n;\n    m._a&#x3D;1;\n    m._b&#x3D;2;\n    n._a&#x3D;3;\n    n._b&#x3D;4;\n    std::cout&lt;&lt;m.add();\n    return 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>我们是。。</p>\n<p>或许我们可以：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-C++\" data-language=\"C++\"><code class=\"language-C++\">class ClassName&#123;\npublic:\n    void init(int a,char b)&#123;\n        _a&#x3D;a;\n        _b&#x3D;b;\n    &#125;\nprivate:\n    int _a;\n    char _b;\n&#125;;</code></pre>\n\n<p>然后我们再调用<code>init</code>函数就能将对象进行初始化。但这样不免还是有些。</p>\n<p>我们更希望在，就像<code>int a=1</code>这样，而不需要再手动调用初始化函数进行赋值。</p>\n<p>C++中，我们就要用到构造函数。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"构造函数\"><a href=\"#构造函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"构造函数\"></a>构造函数</h1><h2 id=\"构造函数的定义\"><a href=\"#构造函数的定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"构造函数的定义\"></a>构造函数的定义</h2><p>构造函数是一个特殊的，名字和类名相同。实例化类时，在生成相应的对象时，保证每个对象都有一个合适的初始值。它在对象的生命周期内。</p>\n<p>我们要定义中的这几点：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>构造函数的函数名与类名相同。</li>\n<li>无返回值，所以不写返回值。</li>\n<li>编译器会在实例化时自动调用。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>下面我们使用构造函数来简化上面例子中对象的初始化。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-C++\" data-language=\"C++\"><code class=\"language-C++\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\nclass MyClass&#123;\npublic:\n    int _a;\n    char _b;\n    int add()&#123;\n        return (_a+_b);\n    &#125;\n    MyClass(int a,char b)&#123;\n        _a&#x3D;a;\n        _b&#x3D;b;\n    &#125;\n&#125;;\nint main()&#123;\n    MyClass m(1,2),n(3,4);\n    std::cout&lt;&lt;m.add();\n    return 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>值得注意的是，构造函数必须是，不然编译器会报错！</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>当然，构造函数不仅可以进行成员变量的初始化。任何你想在实例化类时进行的操作都可以放在构造函数里面。</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"使用初始化列表\"><a href=\"#使用初始化列表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用初始化列表\"></a>使用初始化列表</h2><p>对类中的成员进行初始化，上面的构造函数还是有些不简洁。。</p>\n<p>还是上面的例子，下面是使用初始化列表的构造函数：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">MyClass(int a,char b):_a(a),_b(b)&#123;&#x2F;*其他操作*&#x2F;&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>这样构造函数看起来就很简洁。</p>\n<p>使用初始化列表要注意初始化的顺序，和列表中变量的顺序无关，如下面的程序：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/cpp/2/9.jpg\"></p>\n<p>上面的程序按理来说应该输出1，但是实际结果与预想的不同。</p>\n<p>由于<code>_a</code>在类中先声明，所以先被初始化的应该是<code>_a</code>。这时候将还没有初始化<code>_b</code>的值赋给<code>_a</code>，所以最后输出的就是初始化前<code>_b</code>的值，是一个随机的值。</p>\n<h2 id=\"重载和缺省参数\"><a href=\"#重载和缺省参数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"重载和缺省参数\"></a>重载和缺省参数</h2><p>构造函数是支持<mark>重载和缺省参数</mark>的，这使得它的用法更加灵活。</p>\n<h3 id=\"构造函数的重载\"><a href=\"#构造函数的重载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"构造函数的重载\"></a>构造函数的重载</h3><p>我们可以定义多个构造函数，它们！</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-C++\" data-language=\"C++\"><code class=\"language-C++\">class MyClass&#123;\npublic:\n    int _a;\n    char _b;\n    MyClass(int a,char b):_a(a),_b(b)&#123;&#125;\n    MyClass(int a):_a(a),_b(2)&#123;&#125;\n    MyClass(char b):_a(1),_b(b)&#123;&#125;\n&#125;;</code></pre>\n\n<p>这样编译器会。</p>\n<h3 id=\"构造函数缺省参数\"><a href=\"#构造函数缺省参数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"构造函数缺省参数\"></a>构造函数缺省参数</h3><p>我们也可以给某些形参一个：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/cpp/2/10.jpg\"></p>\n<p>构造函数的重载和缺省参数与一般的函数一样，很容易理解，所以不再赘述。当两者都能达到目的时，一般情况下还是推荐使用重载，因为省略参数还对参数列表的顺序有要求。</p>\n<h2 id=\"注意事项\"><a href=\"#注意事项\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意事项\"></a>注意事项</h2><ol>\n<li><p>如果我们没有定义构造函数，编译器会自动加上一个空的构造函数。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>如果实例化类时，如下：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-C++\" data-language=\"C++\"><code class=\"language-C++\">class MyClass&#123;\npublic:\n    int _a;char _b;\n    MyClass():_a(1),_b(2)&#123;&#125;\n&#125;;\nint main()&#123;\n    MyClass m;&#x2F;&#x2F;MyClass m();\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>读者可以先想一想上面代码存在的问题。</p>\n<p><code>MyClass m()</code>似乎是一个合乎情理的写法，然而我们仔细观察一下，就会发现：是的，编译器会将该语句理解为一个作用域在main函数内的函数的声明，而不会将m识别为一个类类型的变量。当我们使用m时，编译器报错：</p>\n<p>我们正确的做法应该不加括号！</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"析构函数\"><a href=\"#析构函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"析构函数\"></a>析构函数</h1><p>同构造函数类似，析构函数在销毁对象时会被编译器自动调用。</p>\n<h2 id=\"析构函数的定义\"><a href=\"#析构函数的定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"析构函数的定义\"></a>析构函数的定义</h2><p>析构函数(destructor) 与构造函数相反，，如对象所在的函数已调用完毕，系统就会自动执行析构函数。析构函数往往用来做的工作。</p>\n<p>但是注意析构函数不是用来销毁对象的，而是在对象的生命周期结束，对象被销毁的时候用来清理残余资源的。</p>\n<p><strong>析构函数的特征如下</strong>：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>析构函数的函数名时类名前面加上<code>~</code>。</li>\n<li>无返回值。</li>\n<li>析构函数不能有参数！</li>\n<li>编译器在对象销毁时自动调用。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"析构函数的实例\"><a href=\"#析构函数的实例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"析构函数的实例\"></a>析构函数的实例</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-C++\" data-language=\"C++\"><code class=\"language-C++\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\nclass MyClass&#123;\npublic:\n    int _a;char _b;\n    MyClass():_a(1),_b(2)&#123;&#125;\n    ~MyClass()&#123;std::cout&lt;&lt;&quot;调用了析构函数&quot;;&#125;\n&#125;;\nint main()&#123;\n    MyClass m;\n    return 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>(即main函数结束，所有资源被释放)，输出。<br><br></p>\n<p>这个例子，但还不能体现出清理资源这一点。</p>\n<br>\n\n<p>我们再看看下面的例子（以教材的实现string类为例）：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-C++\" data-language=\"C++\"><code class=\"language-C++\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\n#include &lt;cstdlib&gt;\nclass String&#123;\nprivate:\n    char* _p;\n    int _size;\npublic:\n    String(int n);\n    ~String();\n&#125;;\nString::String(int n&#x3D;5):_size(n)&#123;\n    std::cout&lt;&lt;&quot;调用了构造函数&quot;&lt;&lt;&#39;\\n&#39;;\n    _p &#x3D; (char*)malloc(n*sizeof(char));\n&#125;\nString::~String()&#123;\n    std::cout&lt;&lt;&quot;调用了析构函数&quot;&lt;&lt;&#39;\\n&#39;;\n    free (_p);\n&#125;\nint main()&#123;\n    String s;\n    return 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>输出：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">调用了构造函数\n调用了析构函数</code></pre>\n\n<p>这个例子就比较完善了。我们在实例化string类时，；string对象销毁时，。</p>\n<h2 id=\"析构函数的意义\"><a href=\"#析构函数的意义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"析构函数的意义\"></a>析构函数的意义</h2><p>析构函数的意义就是释放多余的空间。</p>\n<p>我们给对象的成员动态分配了空间。。但是指向它的指针已经被销毁，所以。如果程序一直这样运行下去，内存垃圾越来越多，程序就会运行地越来越慢，最后可能会导致电脑死机。所以我们需要析构函数来帮我们自动化地解决这个问题。</p>\n<hr>\n","text":"引言上一节中我们举了这样一个例子： #include &lt;iostream&gt; class MyClass&#123; public: int _a; char _b; int add()&#123; return (_a+_b); &#125; &#125;; int ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.3k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"专业课内","slug":"专业课内","count":28,"path":"api/categories/专业课内.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"C++程序设计","slug":"C-程序设计","count":9,"path":"api/tags/C-程序设计.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BC%95%E8%A8%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">引言</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">构造函数</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">构造函数的定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">使用初始化列表</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%87%8D%E8%BD%BD%E5%92%8C%E7%BC%BA%E7%9C%81%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">重载和缺省参数</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%BD%BD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">构造函数的重载</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%BC%BA%E7%9C%81%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">构造函数缺省参数</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">注意事项</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9E%90%E6%9E%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">析构函数</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9E%90%E6%9E%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">析构函数的定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9E%90%E6%9E%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">析构函数的实例</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9E%90%E6%9E%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">析构函数的意义</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Satoing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"iconfont icon-bilibili-fill","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/52750318"},"Leetcode":{"icon":"iconfont icon-leetcode","link":"https://leetcode.cn/u/satoing/"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Minecraft mod服搭建(踩坑向)","uid":"b70cd78dd7d9ecedb37f01e91be98a01","slug":"mod","date":"2022-01-19T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-19T14:00:06.528Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/mod.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/mc/1.jpg","text":"作为从古老版本的MC穿越过来的萌新，搭建自己的Minecraft服务器的确是一件很令人兴奋的事。本篇将重点讲解如何在Linux上借助宝塔面板搭建自己的MC服务器(原生服&amp;mod服)，之后的文章还会讲解再一些mod服上进阶操作及模组推荐（摸索中……）。 说在前面 我的服务器...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"兴趣","slug":"兴趣","count":4,"path":"api/categories/兴趣.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Minecraft","slug":"Minecraft","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Minecraft.json"}],"author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Satoing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"iconfont icon-bilibili-fill","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/52750318"},"Leetcode":{"icon":"iconfont icon-leetcode","link":"https://leetcode.cn/u/satoing/"}}}}},"next_post":{"title":"2.2类的存储模型和This指针","uid":"3ceb65e3bb2a922a6ceb539e5948d9e2","slug":"cpp2.2","date":"2022-01-16T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-21T05:14:53.552Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/cpp2.2.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/cpp/cover1.jpg","text":"引言本节我们将学习C++中类的存储模型，据此更好地讲解this指针及其作用。由于C++的类和C语言中的结构体大致相当，所以我们先回顾C中结构体的存储方式，即。 先看个例子学习C语言时，我们可能了解过。它是结构体的成员进行存储时采用的方式。比如，对于下面这样一个结构体： typed...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.5k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"专业课内","slug":"专业课内","count":28,"path":"api/categories/专业课内.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"C++程序设计","slug":"C-程序设计","count":9,"path":"api/tags/C-程序设计.json"}],"author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Satoing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"iconfont icon-bilibili-fill","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/52750318"},"Leetcode":{"icon":"iconfont icon-leetcode","link":"https://leetcode.cn/u/satoing/"}}}}}}